snippet.title: Witchfall: Secrets of Emotica // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1686780/Witchfall_Secrets_of_Emotica

Welcome to the world of Witchfall, a magical land filled with adventure! Play as five adorable critters: Koemi, Rez, Maya, Sloberg or Envel as they embark on a perilous journey to stop the evil Professor Flitz from stealing the mysterious Emotica Shards.

Developed by BaconFish Games
